label: Topics in Nutrition Research
description: Series of one-third term intensive courses on current topics in nutritional sciences research. Same as ANSC 525 and FSHN 510. May be repeated in the same term to a maximum of 3 hours. Prerequisite: Advanced Biochemistry.
